Sentencas: A layered perovskite oxide, GdBaCoFeO5+x (GBCF), was investigated as a novel cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBaCoFeO5+x as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A laboratory-sized Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 (SDC)-based tri-layer cell of NiO-SDC/SDC/GBCF was tested under intermediate-temperature conditions of 550-650 degrees C with humidified H-2 (similar to 3% H2O) as a fuel and the static ambient air as oxidant.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBaCoFeO5+x as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A maximal power density of 746 mW cm(-2) was achieved at 650 C. The interfacial polarization resistance was as low as 0.42, 0.18 and 0.11 Omega cm(2) at 550, 600 and 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBaCoFeO5+x as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The experimental results indicate that the layered perovskite GBCF is a promising cathode candidate for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBaCoFeO5+x as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Published by Elsevier Ltd on behalf of Professor T. Nejat Veziroglu.
Titulo: Layered perovskite GdBaCoFeO5+x as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
